ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This grouping of value sets identifies patients who have a diagnosis of an infection.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have a diagnosis of an infection. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Diagnosis category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes which represent infection as defined by the measure steward. Codes used are to be ICD10PCS, ICD9 or SNOMED-CT codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: These include codes for fungal infections, viral infections and infections that are not documented as current or active.)
